description: Eleven-color screenprint bleed printed with visually irregular borders. The image includes drawings and marks by the artist made on Denril, overhead projector film and Rubylith film, and a halftoned image manipulated by the artist. It is signed and dated 2011 by the artist in pencil on the border and in the image in ink 2010.
